channel.title: Website Logo
channel.description:
I'm about to finish my A+ Certification, which is (if you didn't know) telling everyone you're awesome at computer repair hire me blah blah blah blah blah, and I'm working on the website now. It will, OMG RLY?, be about computer repair. I need a logo and as I'm not very creative, I'm not capable of producing something of interest to the eye :P
So, colors at the moment don't really matter. Perhaps something with blue and another color. A complicated set of text is not necessary. An image of a computer in some way would be nice (<-- This is mainly my problem). If you need to know the company name, let me know. Otherwise, if I could have the PSD, that'd be awesome. And it should be like.. something you'd think would fit in the top corner of a webpage, somethin' like that.
Any further questions, let me know.
Thanks a bunch.
